完全少女論
Kanjou Shoujoron (Full Theory of a Girl)

95
00:11:16,409 --> 00:11:19,409
作詞・作曲：北澤伸一郎
Lyrics/Composition: Shinichiro Kitazawa

96
00:11:30,409 --> 00:11:34,409
あー 君が好きな服
Ah, the clothes you like

97
00:11:34,409 --> 00:11:37,409
濡れたままだね
Are still soaking wet

98
00:11:37,909 --> 00:11:40,909
こんな夜だから
Because it's a night like this

99
00:11:40,909 --> 00:11:43,909
響かせてミュージック
