110
00:12:24,409 --> 00:12:27,909
もっと確かめてみて
Try to check even more

111
00:12:41,909 --> 00:12:45,409
ねえ 朝が来る前に
Hey, before morning comes

112
00:12:45,409 --> 00:12:48,909
連れ出してみて
Try to take me out

113
00:12:48,909 --> 00:12:52,409
こんな夜だから
Because it's a night like this

114
00:12:52,409 --> 00:12:55,909
鳴り止まないミュージック
The music won't stop ringing

115
00:12:55,909 --> 00:13:00,409
お気に入りの曲は
To your favorite track

116
00:13:00,409 --> 00:13:03,409
君は踊らない
You don't dance

117
00:13:03,909 --> 00:13:06,909
君だけ踊らない
Only you don't dance

118
00:13:11,909 --> 00:13:15,409
感情論で君を傷つけて
Hurting you with emotional theories

119
00:13:15,409 --> 00:13:18,909
こんなひと嫌いになるでしょ
You'll start to hate someone like this, right?

120
00:13:18,909 --> 00:13:22,409
純情なんて 呆れるくらいに
Pure innocence, to an amazing degree

121
00:13:22,409 --> 00:13:25,409
本当似合わないけど
Really doesn't suit me, but

122
00:13:25,409 --> 00:13:28,909
テンションちょっと 上げて知らんぷり
Raising the tension a bit and playing dumb

123
00:13:28,909 --> 00:13:32,409
困らせたい そんな気分よ
I want to trouble you, that's the mood

124
00:13:32,409 --> 00:13:35,909
単純じゃんって 言われたくないよ
I don't want you to say it's simple

125
00:13:35,909 --> 00:13:39,409
きっとわがままだけど
I'm sure I'm being selfish, but

126
00:13:39,409 --> 00:13:45,909
完全少女論 自己中心度 気分上昇度 いいじゃんこれで
Theory of a Full Girl: Egotism, mood swings... isn't this fine?

127
00:13:45,909 --> 00:13:52,409
不全純情度 未完成情緒 一言論外でしょ
Imperfect innocence, incomplete emotions... it's out of the question, right?

128
