139
00:14:33,909 --> 00:14:36,909
もっと確かめてみる
I'll try to check even more

140
00:15:01,287 --> 00:15:02,087
はぁ……
(Sigh)

141
00:15:02,787 --> 00:15:05,587
さっきのは……なんだったんだろう
What was that just now...?

142
00:15:06,587 --> 00:15:14,587
たくさんの人たちと、その人たちが発する熱気に包まれて、私はすごくワクワクしてた
Surrounded by so many people and the heat they emitted, I was really excited.

143
00:15:15,587 --> 00:15:18,587
別だかすごく懐かしい感じがした……
It felt somehow very nostalgic...

144
00:15:20,887 --> 00:15:23,587
ねえねえ、キミ、大丈夫？
Hey, hey, you okay?

145
00:15:23,887 --> 00:15:24,587
え？
Eh?

146
00:15:24,887 --> 00:15:28,087
なんか顔色が良くなかったからさ
You didn't look very well.

147
00:15:28,287 --> 00:15:31,587
あ、うちはミオだよ。占い師をやってる
Oh, I'm Mio. I'm a fortune teller.

148
00:15:31,887 --> 00:15:36,587
ん、キミ、何かを探してるね。そう占いにでてる
Hmm, you're looking for something. That's what the fortune says.

149
00:15:36,887 --> 00:15:38,287
わかるの？
You can tell?

150
00:15:38,587 --> 00:15:43,587
うん、よかったら話してみて、何か力になれるかもしれないし
Yeah, if you'd like, try talking to me. I might be able to help.

151
00:15:44,087 --> 00:15:45,587
実は……
Actually...

152
00:15:48,587 --> 00:15:52,087
なるほど……キミは『オンガク』を探してるんだね
I see... You're looking for "Music".

153
00:15:53,087 --> 00:15:56,087
それならあそこに行ってみればいいんじゃない？
In that case, why don't you try going over there?

154
00:15:56,587 --> 00:16:00,587
世界の果てにあるっていう、光の塔
The Tower of Light, which is said to be at the edge of the world.

155
00:16:01,087 --> 00:16:05,587
そこには天使が住んでて、やってきた人の願いを叶えてくれるんだって
They say an angel lives there, and they grant the wishes of those who visit.

156
00:16:06,087 --> 00:16:11,587
だからそこに行ってお願いをすれば、キミの探しものも見つかるんじゃないかな
So if you go there and make a wish, maybe you'll find what you're looking for.

157
00:16:12,087 --> 00:16:15,587
親切にありがとう、そこに行ってみることにするよ！
Thank you for your kindness, I'll try going there!

158
00:16:16,087 --> 00:16:19,587
どういたしまして。でもお礼なんていらないって
You're welcome. But I told you, you don't need to thank me.

159
00:16:19,887 --> 00:16:21,087
ん？
Hm?

160
00:16:21,587 --> 00:16:24,587
だってうちは……キミのことが大好きだから！
Because I... love you!

161
00:16:25,087 --> 00:16:28,087
ずっとずっと前からね！
Since a long, long time ago!

162
00:16:39,087 --> 00:16:45,087
コトダマ紡ぐ未来
作詞：石川泰 作曲：田辺トシノ
Kotodama Tsumugu Mirai
Lyrics: Yasushi Ishikawa Composition: Toshino Tanabe

163
00:17:01,887 --> 00:17:07,587
遥か 遠く 続く
Far, far away, continuing...

164
00:17:08,087 --> 00:17:13,587
果てなき道
...an endless road.

165
00:17:14,287 --> 00:17:19,087
それでも いつか
Even so, someday...

166
00:17:19,587 --> 00:17:25,887
辿り着くと信じて
...believing that I will arrive.

167
00:17:26,587 --> 00:17:31,587
たとえ 今は
Even if now...

168
00:17:32,087 --> 00:17:38,087
辛く 厳しくても
...is hard and painful.

169
00:17:38,887 --> 00:17:43,587
小さな 笑顔 守る
Protecting a small smile...

170
00:17:44,087 --> 00:17:51,287
全て捧げて
...giving everything.

171
00:17:51,887 --> 00:17:57,087
心 重なる
Hearts overlapping...

172
00:17:57,587 --> 00:18:03,887
言葉より強い絆に
...in a bond stronger than words.

173
00:18:04,287 --> 00:18:09,587
染め上げていく
Dyeing it all...

174
00:18:10,087 --> 00:18:16,287
ひとつになる鼓動で
...with a heartbeat that becomes one.

175
00:18:20,087 --> 00:18:25,587
記憶辿る 追憶の旅 続けて
Tracing memories, continuing the journey of reminiscence.

176
00:18:31,587 --> 00:18:37,087
あらゆることを 受け止めるから
Because I'll accept everything...

177
00:18:37,587 --> 00:18:43,587
言葉はいらないの
...words are not needed.

178
00:18:44,287 --> 00:18:51,087
それは 永遠に
That is eternally...

179
00:19:02,087 --> 00:19:07,287
いつも 近く そばで
Always near, by your side...

180
00:19:07,587 --> 00:19:13,887
見ていたけど
...I was watching.

181
00:19:14,587 --> 00:19:19,087
気づかずに いても
Even if I didn't notice...

182
00:19:19,587 --> 00:19:26,587
今は 遠く感じる
...now it feels far away.

183
00:19:27,587 --> 00:19:33,087
あとを 追いかけ
Chasing after you...

184
00:19:33,587 --> 00:19:39,587
絆から愛に変われば
...if the bond turns into love.

185
00:19:40,087 --> 00:19:45,087
染め上げていく
Dyeing it all...

186
00:19:45,587 --> 00:19:52,587
二人だけの秘密
...a secret just between the two of us.

187
00:19:54,887 --> 00:20:01,087
想いを込めた 言葉の強さ 信じて
Believing in the strength of words filled with feelings.

188
00:20:03,102 --> 00:20:05,202
…見てる
...Watching

189
00:20:07,052 --> 00:20:09,002
うちに秘めたとき
When I kept it inside

190
00:20:09,102 --> 00:20:11,602
覚悟していた
I was prepared

191
00:20:12,202 --> 00:20:16,602
未来を紡ぐために
In order to spin the future

192
00:20:43,102 --> 00:20:45,402
気が付けばほら
If you notice, look

193
00:20:45,602 --> 00:20:48,102
心に宿る
It dwells in my heart

194
00:20:48,402 --> 00:20:55,102
ともしび
A lamp

195
00:20:55,602 --> 00:20:57,902
小さな光
A small light

196
00:20:58,202 --> 00:21:00,502
寄り添い合えば
If we snuggle up together

197
00:21:01,302 --> 00:21:06,102
そう　未来を指して
Yes, pointing to the future

198
00:21:07,902 --> 00:21:10,502
青く広がる
Spreading blue

199
00:21:10,702 --> 00:21:13,602
晴れ渡る空
A clear sky

200
00:21:14,402 --> 00:21:19,902
見上げる
Looking up

201
00:21:20,402 --> 00:21:24,102
もう言葉すら
Already, even words

202
00:21:24,302 --> 00:21:26,602
いらないから
Aren't needed anymore

203
00:21:27,002 --> 00:21:31,302
ただ　抱きしめていて
Just keep holding me

204
00:21:32,702 --> 00:21:38,402
時は永遠に
Time is eternal

205
00:22:07,202 --> 00:22:10,502
降り注ぐ雨のような歓声
(Cheers like pouring rain)

206
00:22:11,302 --> 00:22:18,602
その中で、煌びやかな服を着たあたしは、幸せそうな笑顔で手を振っている
(In the midst of that, wearing glittering clothes, I wave with a happy smile)

207
00:22:19,502 --> 00:22:23,602
（まるでもう一人のあたしのように）
(As if it were another me)

208
00:22:25,602 --> 00:22:28,902
世界の果てにあるという光の塔
The Tower of Light, said to be at the edge of the world

209
00:22:29,602 --> 00:22:35,102
『オンガク』を探すために、あたしはそこを目指すことに決めた
To find "Music," I decided to head there

210
00:22:35,902 --> 00:22:41,302
何日かかるかわからないけど、幸いなことに時間はたくさんある
I don't know how many days it'll take, but fortunately, I have plenty of time

211
00:22:42,102 --> 00:22:43,902
ただ……
Only...

212
00:22:44,102 --> 00:22:47,302
お腹、空いた……
(Stomach growling) I'm hungry...

213
00:22:49,002 --> 00:22:49,902
あ
Ah

214
00:22:50,102 --> 00:22:53,102
なんでわためを見てお腹を鳴らしてるの！？
Why is your stomach growling while looking at Watame!?

215
00:22:54,102 --> 00:22:58,302
え、わかんないけど、なんか君を見たら急に
Eh, I don't know, but looking at you just made me suddenly...

216
00:22:59,102 --> 00:23:01,602
わためは『非常食』じゃないよ〜！
Watame isn't "emergency food"!

217
00:23:02,102 --> 00:23:06,102
見逃してくれたら、代わりにわためが歌うから〜
If you let me go, Watame will sing for you instead!

218
00:23:08,102 --> 00:23:09,602
……歌？
...Singing?

219
00:23:10,602 --> 00:23:12,602
歌って……何？
Singing... what is that?

220
00:23:13,602 --> 00:23:16,102
え、君、歌を知らないの？
Eh, you don't know about singing?

221
00:23:17,102 --> 00:23:20,602
よーし、じゃあわためが教えてあげるよ。
Alright, then Watame will teach you.

222
00:23:21,102 --> 00:23:23,602
歌っていうのはね……
Singing is, you see...

223
00:23:35,102 --> 00:23:37,602
滅びてゆくこのステラ
This stella is perishing

224
00:23:37,702 --> 00:23:40,502
絆を辿るストーリー
A story tracing bonds

225
00:23:40,702 --> 00:23:42,702
受け継ぐ想いが
May the inherited feelings

226
00:23:42,902 --> 00:23:45,602
生まれ変われますように
Be reborn

227
00:23:57,102 --> 00:24:00,102
目の前 現れた無表情は
The expressionless face that appeared before me

228
00:24:00,302 --> 00:24:07,302
誰にも懐を見せないまま
Without showing its heart to anyone

229
00:24:08,102 --> 00:24:13,102
事象が世界を歪ませて
Events distort the world

230
00:24:13,302 --> 00:24:18,602
光がただ眩しすぎた
The light was just too bright

231
00:24:19,102 --> 00:24:21,602
燦々と照りつける
Shining brilliantly

232
00:24:21,702 --> 00:24:24,102
荒野に残した足跡
Footprints left in the wasteland

233
00:24:25,102 --> 00:24:27,102
与えられたのなら
If it was given to us

234
00:24:27,202 --> 00:24:29,602
守るものだけ
Only things to protect

235
00:24:29,902 --> 00:24:32,302
滅びてゆくこのステラ
This stella is perishing

236
00:24:32,402 --> 00:24:35,102
叶うことがないとしても
Even if it never comes true

237
00:24:35,202 --> 00:24:37,902
変えよう 世界を
Let's change the world

238
00:24:38,102 --> 00:24:40,602
灯してゆく
Keeping it lit

239
00:24:40,902 --> 00:24:43,502
震える手が弾いた
Trembling hands plucked

240
00:24:43,602 --> 00:24:46,102
意味を持たない銃口
A meaningless muzzle

241
00:24:46,602 --> 00:24:48,902
輝く星の下
Under the shining stars

242
00:24:49,102 --> 00:24:52,602
私は今 息をする
I am breathing now

243
00:24:57,102 --> 00:25:01,602
それなら あなたは騙したんだ
In that case, you deceived me

244
00:25:03,094 --> 00:25:05,094
breath of stella

245
00:25:03,144 --> 00:25:04,894
今なら
If it's now

246
00:25:05,694 --> 00:25:08,194
全て分かってしまう
I'll understand everything

247
00:25:08,794 --> 00:25:10,194
名前を
Your name...

248
00:25:10,594 --> 00:25:13,194
呼んでくれていても
even if you're calling it

249
00:25:13,594 --> 00:25:15,494
私に
to me...

250
00:25:16,594 --> 00:25:18,994
届けられていなかった
it wasn't being delivered

251
00:25:19,594 --> 00:25:21,494
消える日の前でただ
Just before the day it disappears

252
00:25:21,894 --> 00:25:24,394
立ち尽くして煙る灰
standing still, smoking ash

253
00:25:24,894 --> 00:25:26,994
命の理屈がいま
The logic of life now

254
00:25:27,494 --> 00:25:29,594
答えをせまる
demands an answer

255
00:25:30,194 --> 00:25:32,294
滅びてゆくその中で
Within that which is perishing

256
00:25:32,794 --> 00:25:34,994
息を凝らした分くらい
about as much as I held my breath

257
00:25:35,394 --> 00:25:37,494
解れた絆を
the unraveled bonds

258
00:25:37,994 --> 00:25:40,394
振り解いて
shaking them off

259
00:25:40,794 --> 00:25:43,094
お願いどうかそばにいて
Please, somehow stay by my side

260
00:25:43,494 --> 00:25:45,594
声が銃声に求めた
My voice sought it in the gunshot

261
00:25:45,994 --> 00:25:48,094
終わりと始まりの
Of the end and the beginning

262
00:25:48,494 --> 00:25:50,894
時の中で
within the time

263
00:25:50,994 --> 00:25:57,094
Ah...

264
00:26:02,894 --> 00:26:06,494
瞳の奥に映った
Reflected in the depths of your eyes

265
00:26:07,994 --> 00:26:10,494
壊れかけている
broken and crumbling

266
00:26:10,794 --> 00:26:13,294
心に持つ
held in the heart

267
00:26:13,794 --> 00:26:15,794
引き金に
on the trigger

268
00:26:16,194 --> 00:26:18,194
かけた指
the finger placed

269
00:26:18,594 --> 00:26:21,194
先が示す未来を
the future shown ahead

270
00:26:21,594 --> 00:26:24,594
祈るだろう
I will pray for it

271
00:26:24,694 --> 00:26:26,594
Ah...

272
00:26:26,994 --> 00:26:29,194
滅びてゆくこのステラ
This Stella that is perishing

273
00:26:29,494 --> 00:26:31,694
瞬きの数の傷
Scars numbering as many as blinks

274
00:26:31,994 --> 00:26:34,494
心がこのまま
Even if my heart remains this way

275
00:26:34,994 --> 00:26:37,394
途絶えてしまっても
and ceases to be

276
00:26:37,794 --> 00:26:39,894
私の生まれた理由も
The reason I was born, too

277
00:26:40,194 --> 00:26:42,594
手放さないでお願い
please don't let go of it

278
00:26:42,794 --> 00:26:45,194
終わりと始まりの
Of the end and the beginning

279
00:26:45,494 --> 00:26:47,694
時の中で
within the time

280
00:26:47,894 --> 00:26:55,594
Ah...

281
00:26:56,994 --> 00:26:59,594
私はここにいるよ
I am here

282
00:26:59,994 --> 00:27:02,594
何度でも確かめられるよ
I can confirm it as many times as it takes

283
00:27:02,994 --> 00:27:05,394
心の存在と名前を
The existence of the heart and my name

284
00:27:05,894 --> 00:27:08,194
あなたが生き抜いた世界は
The world you lived through

285
00:27:08,494 --> 00:27:10,794
まだ私の中で息をする
still breathes within me

286
00:27:33,594 --> 00:27:39,594
光、光、光
Light, light, light

287
00:27:40,794 --> 00:27:47,294
その星のような煌めきが――頭に焼き付いて離れない
That star-like shimmer—is burned into my mind and won't leave.

288
00:27:48,394 --> 00:27:52,294
あの子がやっていたことは何なんだろう？
What was that girl doing?

289
00:27:52,994 --> 00:27:59,194
「ウタ」にって言ってたけど……初めて聞く言葉だ
She said 'uta' (song)... it's the first time I've heard that word.

290
00:27:59,894 --> 00:28:07,294
だけどウタは、あたしの心の深いところに確かに染み込んできた……
But the song certainly soaked into the deep parts of my heart...

291
00:28:10,494 --> 00:28:13,094
静かだなぁ……
It's quiet...

292
00:28:13,494 --> 00:28:18,594
この世界は、ずっと静寂に包まれている
This world has always been shrouded in silence.

293
00:28:18,994 --> 00:28:27,094
だけどさっきのあれは――「ウタ」は、そのどれとも違った
But that thing just now—the 'song'—was different from any of that.

294
00:28:27,994 --> 00:28:30,594
あれは、何なんだろう……
What was that...

295
00:28:30,994 --> 00:28:37,594
あと別れ際にくれたこの頭につける道具は……？遺物……？
And this tool for my head she gave me as we parted...? An artifact...?

296
00:28:40,994 --> 00:28:45,094
確か「ヘッドセット」って言ってた
I think she called it a 'headset'.

297
00:28:45,994 --> 00:28:52,094
これを使えば……あたしも「歌」えるんだろうか
If I use this... I wonder if I can 'sing' too.

298
00:29:01,994 --> 00:29:04,394
forever has gone,

299
00:29:05,494 --> 00:29:08,494
today is infinity

300
00:29:08,794 --> 00:29:11,594
